This story starts at Twilights castle.\.\.\. Recently Twilight faced yet another change in her life. After years, one of her dearest friends, Sunset Shimmer, finally came back to Equestria again.

Why you might ask?\.\.\. Well in the human world \.\.(and I mean completely human, \.\.because\.\. you know.\| 'Anthros' and stuff in here)\.\.\. her powers weren‘t needed anymore. \.\.The girls experienced enough challenges together to learn how to use their powers correctly. This worlds Twilight was finally ready to lead the group on her own, giving Sunset the chance to go back home.

Which brings us back to the very moment.\.\.\. It is a beautiful, sunny and very hot summer day in equestria. Everything's peaceful and quiet. \.\.\.However, the heroines  of our story are already preparing their next adventure at Twilight's castle. And here begins our story. I will tell you the story about a group of girls that...
Girls come quick! You have to see this!
Yeah, or you just interrupt me and do it yourself.
Calm down Twilight! \.\.You already sound like Rainbow Dash. *chuckle*
I know, I know. But I‘m just so excited! Look at this!

Indeed, there was something special today. \.\.\.The cutie map, which already sent Twilight and her friends to several places in and beyond Equestria to solve friendship problems, was now glowing with several cutiemarks.
Why does the map call four of us. That’s unusual.\.\.\. I mean, that is too big for a simple 'friendship problem', isn't it?
Yeah, and apparently it only sends unicorns.
Looking at your abilities we should rather say an alicorn and TWO unicorns. *chuckle*
Well, I‘m just glad I don‘t have to do this alone. I wouldn ‘t have been able to do such a mission on my own.
But Starlight is right. \.\.It‘s odd that the map sends my best students and me on a mission.\.\.\. Looks like this might be a tough one.
Trixie, I‘m sure she didn‘t mean you by that.
This is quite far away. Is it even still part of Equestria?
Looks like it‘s at the very border of the country. Look, there‘s still a train leading to it.
These small things look like some old ruins...
Mmh, I think I‘ve seen these before in a book that‘s somewhere in the library.
No we sadly have no time for that. This is why I invited you over, Rarity. \.\.I‘m sorry to ruin your vacation days with that burden, but I need somepony to look up for more infos about that place.
Don‘t worry, darling. I‘m always happy to help my friends. I will take care of everything while you are gone.
Thank you! \|Then we can start our journey.\.\.\. But first we should buy some supplies from town.
.\.\..\.\..\.\.\. *sigh* And where do I start now?
A fallen tree is blocking the path! We cant go there!
We could simply climb over the trunk.
Trust me, Sunset. It‘s better we don’t!
How often do I have to say that that‘s not Applejack?
Let‘s turn around. After the storm last night she‘s probably occupied with her animals anyways.
I don‘t think we have time for that.
